com.bragi.sonify.music

Enum Instrument

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Instrument>
      • com.bragi.sonify.music.Instrument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Instrument>
    Deprecated.

    public enum Instrument
extends java.lang.Enum<Instrument>
    This enum holds constants for all MIDI instruments and their respective keys as given by the MIDI standard. For a further description, refer to: http://soundprogramming.net/file_formats/general_midi_instrument_list
    Author:
    Jan-Christoph Klie
